amendments added by the senate before sending it on to the 
president for his signature approval came with no controversy 
under the bill the maximum sentence for major fraud would be 
set at 10 years in prison 
fines under the measure would be similar to current ones for 
fraud against the government they vary depending on the amount of 
the loss in especially flagrant cases however courts would have 
the option of imposing penalties of up to 10 million under the 
bill 
